{"tid":1214821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共仁濟校長 代表全校表示 沒有學生想參與遊行","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:57:03.000Z","uid":186838,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fb1dd1115007f2c538c43d86fb3cdb7106238b","tid":1214821,"uid":186838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"仁濟醫院第二中學校長<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">余大偉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於文匯報發表言論 <br />\n指學校學生發起聯署係<span style=\"color: blue;\">騎劫學校名義</span>所為，<br />\n你代表你個新界校長會發表意見係可以<br />\n但係你憑咩抹殺所有學生既意見<br />\n屌你老母啦 幾乎全香港人唔止學生都反對修例啦<br />\n點樣製造反對修對修例嘅假象呀你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5wqbhxjo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5wqbhxjo&h=23b70e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/06/08/HK1906080013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2FHK1906080013.htm&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=d2a92270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/06/08/HK1906080013.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1un0d24k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1un0d24k&h=92c371a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tbpwg8k3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftbpwg8k3&h=937d4a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://ntsha.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/第七屆職守_名單19-2-12.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fntsha.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E5%B1%86%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%88_%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE19-2-12.pdf&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=81889bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ntsha.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/第七屆職守_名單19-2-12.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/